Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.77,0:00:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是我的秋千啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.85,0:00:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对太君干了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.10,0:00:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.50,0:00:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么 痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.73,0:00:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐…姐…
